            <div type="translation">
                <p>I am the gate. Whoever enters through me will be saved.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Badly damaged. Very fragmentary. The words εἰμί and εἰσέλθῃ are misspelled. Accents and breathings with errors. The inscription is from Jonh' gospel  (John 10:9). </p>
